RT @club4growth .@RandPaul #PennyPlanBalancedBudget is being voted on in the Senate today. It is the only balanced budget that will receive a vote this year.

@club4growth strongly supports getting our fiscal house in order &amp; issued a #KeyVoteAlert in favor of the bill.

https://www.clubforgrowth.org/key-vote-alert-yes-penny-plan-balanced-budget/ https://twitter.com/RandPaul/status/1135590752271163398 QT @RandPaul We teach our children that money doesn’t grow on trees, and then they grow up watching politicians pretend otherwise. Meanwhile, our debt soars past $22 trillion, endangers our country. Today, the U.S. Senate can vote to put a stop to it and change course. https://www.paul.senate.gov/news/today-us-senate-vote-sen-paul%E2%80%99s-balanced-budget-plan
